summary: Adds a player home to Amber Creek
descriptionHtml:
[b]REQUIRES: FALSKAAR[/b]
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37994/?

[b]Location: Amber Creek, Falskaar, on the edge of town[/b]

This is a small cottage I knocked up in an afternoon for my low level character. It\'s free - just walk right in - and contains a few chests for storage, a double bed, a bathroom (well, a bath and a bucket!), alchemy/enchanting stations and a couple of bookshelves.

Note: I have necessarily altered the navmesh in Falskaar. Tested with a companion and another nearby mod (Whetherstone House) - worked fine.

=================
Installation
=================

Extract the contents of the ZIP folder into your Data folder

=================
Un-Installation:
=================

Uncheck and delete the .esp file.
